// =============================================================================
//  arith.def
//  opcodes for operations when interfacing to simplescalar
// =============================================================================
//  Original Author : Liang-Kai Wang, 5/2007
//  Maintainer:      Mike Anderson 1/2009 
// =============================================================================
//  This file defines operations for an interface with simplescalar (make OS=HW)
//  DEFOP(OP, NUM, ADDRESS) is defined in simplesim-3.0/sim-outorder.c, which
//  includes this file to define arithmetic operations.
//  Please see the README for more info.
//
//  For details about the benchmark, please refer to the following paper:
//
//      Wang, Tsen, Jhalani, Schulte  "Benchmarks and Performance Analysis
//      of Decimal Floating-Point Applications" from IEEE International
//      Conference on Computer Design, Oct 2007.
